transbit.tbits.dql.treecomponents
Class Value

java.lang.Object
  transbit.tbits.dql.treecomponents.Value
All Implemented Interfaces:
DqlConstants
public class Value
extends java.lang.Object
implements DqlConstants

This class encapsulates VALUE of the DQL grammar. A VALUE is the value specified for a given field in the query. It consists of an operator describing its relation with previous value in the constraint and a PARAMETER of the value.

Author:
Karan Gupta
